<h3>How to Generate More Reviews</h3>
<p>Most customers will leave a review if asked at the right time. The right time for pest control is immediately after treatment when relief is highest.</p>
<p><strong>Post-service text message.</strong> Send an automated text 2 hours after treatment. "Hi [Name], thanks for choosing [Company]. Would you mind leaving us a quick Google review? [link]." This single step generates more reviews than any other tactic.</p>
<p><strong>Review cards.</strong> Hand a physical card to the homeowner after treatment. Include a QR code linking directly to your Google review page. Use our <a href="/tools/review-qr-code-generator/">Review QR Code Generator</a> to create one.</p>
<p><strong>Email follow-up.</strong> Send an email 24 hours after service with a review request. Include a direct link to your Google review page.</p>
<p><strong>Respond to every review.</strong> Responding to reviews signals to Google that your business is engaged. It also shows potential customers that you care about feedback. Use our <a href="/tools/review-response-generator/">Review Response Generator</a> for templates.</p>
